      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i'm not alone, i just... it doesn't matter. talking doesn't change the fact that the person i was is gone too. everything just feels so heavy and pointless. like i'm just going through the motions of a life that ended when he died. it's exhausting to pretend that staying here actually matters.",
