      "content": "it's just that \"getting through the moment\" feels like a lifetime of moments i don't even want. every single day is just a repeat of the same emptiness. i look at the empty side of the bed and i just think... why am i even fighting to stay in a world where he isn't? it feels like i'm just lingering in a place where i don't belong anymore.",
